# CyberChatBot — Cybersecurity Awareness Bot

A WPF desktop application built in C# (.NET Framework 4.7.2) that serves as an interactive cybersecurity awareness assistant.
The bot helps users stay safe online through guided chat, a task management system backed by MySQL, a cybersecurity quiz, 
NLP-simulated intent recognition, and a full activity log.

---

## Project Description

CyberChatBot is a multi-part portfolio project (Parts 1, 2, and 3) combining:
- A conversational chatbot with keyword recognition, sentiment detection, and memory
- A task assistant that stores and manages cybersecurity to-do items in a MySQL database
- A cybersecurity mini-game/quiz with 12 questions, immediate feedback, and scoring
- A Natural Language Processing (NLP) simulation that understands varied user phrasing
- An activity log that records every significant action the bot performs

---

