| Visual Studio | 2022 (Community or higher) | https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/ |
| .NET Framework | 4.7.2 | Included with Visual Studio |
| MySQL Community Server | 8.0+ | https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/mysql/ |
